	<h1>Chicken Recipes For Every Day Of The Week<br></h1>
	
	<p>Over here at Recipe Central, we LOVE chicken. It's such a versatile ingredient, and we're here to show you how you can utilize chicken for a meal every day of the week!</p>
	
	<h3>Sunday: Kung Pao Chicken</h3>
	<p>Start your week off with a bang and make this amazing Kung Pao Chicken!</p>
	
	<h3>Monday: Tandoori Chicken</h3>
	<p>Try making this delicious chicken dish on your grill for that extra char!</p>
		
	<h3>Tuesday: Teriyaki Chicken Casserole</h3>
	<p>This new spin on Teriyaki Chicken is one the whol family will love!</p>	

	<h3>Wednesday: Chicken Ham and Leek Pie</h3>
	<p>We could eat this all day, every day. Though we thought we'd recommend this as a Wednesday pick-me-up instead.</p>	

	<h3>Thursday: Chicken Karaage</h3>
	<p>Chicken Karaage, also known as Japanese Fried Chicken, is delicious and will make the kiddos happy too!</p>	
	
	<h3>Friday: Nutty Chicken Curry</h3>
	<p>This quick curry recipe is a great Friday night meal.</p>	
	
	<h3>Saturday: Crock Pot Chicken Baked Tacos</h3>
	<p>Take advantage of your Saturday and start this delicious taco dish early.</p>	
	
	<p>We hope by the end of the week you'll be as crazy for chicken as we are!</p>
	
